<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Can you add 'trace' and 'exceptions' as a supported option for the Soap Client.</p>

<p>For instance:
        $client = new Zend_Soap_Client('wsdl_url',
                array('trace' =&gt; 1, 'exceptions' =&gt; 0));</p>

<p>Returns:
Message: Unknown SOAP client option</p>

<p>It's an easy fix as I've already repaired my local version. I figure this will help others down the line.</p>

